Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.50,0:00:06.29,Opening,,0,0,0,,Ak niečo chceš,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.29,0:00:07.19,Opening,,0,0,0,,čokoľvek…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:09.19,Opening,,0,0,0,,Príď ku mne.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.19,0:00:10.39,Opening,,0,0,0,,Tvoj strážny anjel.
